OL,3,CScotland face Morocco as Tartan Army
OL,4,Chope to progress to knockout stages
OL,6,FScotland are aiming to secure their
OL,7,Fsecond World Cup victory as they take
OL,8,Fon Morocco.
OL,10,FThe Tartan Army are currently at the
OL,11,Ftop of Group C after beating Haiti in
OL,12,Ftheir opening game 1-0, but they still
OL,13,Fhave to beat two top teams to maintain
OL,14,Ftheir position.
OL,16,FA win against Morocco will mean
OL,17,FScotland make it out of a group stage
OL,18,Fof a major tournament for the first
OL,19,Ftime in their history.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
