OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1782042480
OL,3,CScotland face Morocco as Tartan Army
OL,4,Chope to progress to knockout stages
OL,6,FWith a draw, Steve Clarke's team are
OL,7,Fstill in a strong position to qualify.
OL,9,FScotland are ranked 37th in the world,
OL,10,Fwhile Morocco are ranked 6th, just
OL,11,Fbehind their Group C rivals Brazil.
OL,12,FHaiti are ranked 85th.
OL,14,FMorocco and Brazil tied 1-1 in their
OL,15,Fopener.
OL,17,FThe Morocco clash is the last game
OL,18,FScotland plays in Boston before
OL,19,Fheading to Miami to face Brazil on
OL,20,FJune 24.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
