OL,3,CScotland face Morocco as Tartan Army
OL,4,Chope to progress to knockout stages
OL,6,FEarlier on Friday, it was announced
OL,7,Fthat Morocco's captain, Achraf Hakim,
OL,8,Fwill stand trial for rape in France.
OL,10,FAchraf Hakimi, 27, who plays for Paris
OL,11,FSaint-Germain, was accused of raping a
OL,12,F24-year-old woman at his home in the
OL,13,FFrench capital in 2023.
OL,15,FSpeaking ahead of the game, Scotland
OL,16,Fmanager Steve Clarke said: "Against
OL,17,Fdifficult opponents, we have to be
OL,18,Fvery good. We understand that.
OL,26,@xD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
