OL,3,CScotland face Morocco as Tartan Army
OL,4,Chope to progress to knockout stages
OL,6,F"But sometimes the Scottish psyche and
OL,7,Fthe Scottish mentality means we are a
OL,8,Flittle bit more comfortable when we
OL,9,Fare the underdogs.
OL,11,F"We were the favourites against Haiti
OL,12,Fand we found the game a struggle but
OL,13,Fwe managed to win.
OL,15,F"This time we are the underdogs and
OL,16,Fsometimes Scotland prefer it that way."
