OL,3,CScotland face Morocco as Tartan Army
OL,4,Chope to progress to knockout stages
OL,6,FScottish fans' joyous celebrations and
OL,7,Fantics in Boston since their arrival
OL,8,Fahead of their game against Haiti on
OL,9,FJune 14 have attracted significant
OL,10,Fmedia coverage from the US press.
OL,12,FThe mayor of Boston, Michelle Wu, has
OL,13,Fbeen vocal about her support for their
OL,14,Fguests.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
